descriptionMarkdown:
**UPDATED** on 12/16/2024 some hotfix, thanks to @Silver Wolf and @Lodgeinator. 10/24/2024. Update for 2.0 Factorio. This has better U.P.S./F.P.S., space efficiency, and symmetry. In addition it takes less components to build, and the blueprint is smaller. The only thing that can be improved is symmetry/beauty, better space efficiency, and tighter fuel insertion rules. Maybe the D.L.C. will be supported, but for now it is not.

If you like this, check out my "Transportation Book" blueprint: https://factorioprints.com/view/-LlIxhTNFxY7dfMMzexi. It's my best blueprint yet. I spent so many hours designing and testing it.

**This is a book for all your power needs**.
       
It has steam engines, solar farms, and nuclear power plants from various sources. Everything is tileable, except for the circle.

*Note*: Nuclear power plants require power to start, initially, for combinaters and inserters (1 MW), and a certain number of water pumps.
